Tab of Justin Guitars lesson to play intro for Wish You Were Here by Pink Floyd.
I recommend to learn off Justin's linked video but then use this as a quick 
reminder since the video is 10min long and this takes seconds to recognise once you learn.

Link to video lesson: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lJw4hMjlRYw

